NEWS for st-v1.0.0

    This collection release is intended as a stable release of all
    System Transparency components. There are a few new features,
    improved backwards compatibility with systems provisioned using
    older tools tools and conventions, and much improved
    documentation. Some obsolete features with no known usage have
    been deleted.

